## 3. JavaScript for Testimonials Carousel

The testimonials carousel initialization is on lines 106-129:

```javascript
jQuery(document).ready(function($) {		
	// Testimonials carousel
	const testimonialsParams = {
		slidesToShow: 3,
		infinite: true,
		centerMode: true,
		responsive: [
			{
				breakpoint: 1024,
				settings: {
					slidesToShow: 1,
					centerPadding: '8rem',
				}
			},
			{
				breakpoint: 600,
				settings: {
					slidesToShow: 1,
					centerPadding: '1rem',
				}
			}
		]
	};
	initCarousel(testimonialsParams, '.testimonials');
```

The carousel uses a Slick carousel library wrapper (imported via `initCarousel` from the utilities carousel module). It shows 3 slides on desktop in center mode, 1 slide on tablet with 8rem padding, and 1 slide on mobile with 1rem padding.
